OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777363548
OL,3,CKnife crime rates in Essex down by 15%
OL,4,Cover last year as police target
OL,5,Chotspots
OL,7,FKnife crime rates in Essex have fallen
OL,8,Fby more than 15% in the last year,
OL,9,Faccording to police.
OL,11,FEssex Police recorded 858 serious
OL,12,Fviolence incidents involving knives
OL,13,Fover the past 12 months, which
OL,14,Fcompared with 1,021 the previous year.
OL,16,FThe force said the figures were a
OL,17,Fresult of it focussing on patrol
OL,18,Fhotspots - where serious violence is
OL,19,Flikely to occur - including Tilbury,
OL,20,FSouthend and Basildon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
