OL,3,CKnife crime rates in Essex down by 15%
OL,4,Cover last year as police target
OL,5,Chotspots
OL,7,FEssex Police Superintendent Neal
OL,8,FMiller said the force is "relentlessly
OL,9,Ffocused on those who carry knives,
OL,10,Fthose who use violence, and on
OL,11,Fprotecting communities from harm".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
