PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777363548
OL,3,CKnife crime rates in Essex down by 15%
OL,4,Cover last year as police target
OL,5,Chotspots
OL,7,FHe added: "At the same time, we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to prevention and that means
OL,9,Fworking with partners to identify
OL,10,Fpeople at risk and steer them away
OL,11,Ffrom choices that could have life
OL,12,Fchanging consequences."
OL,14,FThe force said it detected so-called
OL,15,Fhotspots through detailed analysis of
OL,16,Fcrime data, so that officers are
OL,17,Fdeployed to areas where knife crime is
OL,18,Fconcentrated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
