CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777363548
OL,3,CKnife crime rates in Essex down by 15%
OL,4,Cover last year as police target
OL,5,Chotspots
OL,7,FSupt Miller said: "This data led
OL,8,Fapproach allows is to place the right
OL,9,Fofficers, in the right places, at the
OL,10,Fright times.
OL,12,F"It allows us to anticipate risk,
OL,13,Fintervene early and ultimately disrupt
OL,14,Fthe circumstances which enable crime.
OL,16,F"We want to target the causes, not the
OL,17,Fsymptoms."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
